title: No. 1 Center Dedich the Focus of Several
text:
No. 1 Center Justin Dedich the Focus of Several Brandon Huffman 2:30 PM / Originally published on Scout Football Temecula (Calif.) Chaparral center Justin Dedich, the top center nationally in 2018, is close to 20 offers and the focus of a number of programs. TCU was a recent one. 
Temecula (Calif.) Chaparral center Justin Dedich is the top center nationally in the 2018 class and has the offers to validate his standing. 
The four-star has 18 offers, with Oklahoma State , New Mexico , TCU , Kansas and Utah his most recent offers. 
Dedich has also been talking with Stanford and USC and he's visiting Colorado and UCLA this spring, having visited Washington last month. 
He talked at the Under Armour All-America Camp this past weekend about the latest in his recruitment. Share on Facebook
